data.description: Welcome to this charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a den, boasting just under 1600 square feet of comfortable living space. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the attention to detail and the inviting atmosphere created by the choice of flooring, tile or laminate, that spans throughout the entire house. The heart of this home is its stunning kitchen. It's a culinary enthusiast's dream come true, featuring beautiful granite countertops that offer both durability and elegance. The 42-inch cabinets provide ample storage space, while the matching cabinet pantry ensures that all your kitchen essentials are neatly organized. Whether you're cooking for yourself or entertaining guests, this kitchen is sure to impress. One of the standout features of this home is its focus on safety and aesthetics. Impact glass windows not only provide added security but also allow natural light to flood the interior, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. The glass front door not only enhances the curb appeal but also offers a glimpse of the stylish interior as you approach. The spacious open floor plan makes this home feel even larger than its square footage suggests. The living area seamlessly flows into the dining and kitchen spaces, making it ideal for both daily living and entertaining. A tray ceiling with molding adds an extra touch of sophistication to the space, providing a sense of depth and character. In addition to the main living areas, this home offers a den that can serve as a home office, a cozy reading nook, or even a guest bedroom. Its versatility allows you to tailor this space to suit your specific needs. With its modern amenities, stylish finishes, and thoughtful design, this 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a den is a perfect blend of comfort and elegance, offering a wonderful place to call home.
